1. Version 0.2

- Don't like current PDU packing/unpacking mechanism using the pdu_type/1 
  function.

  Consider creating a pack/unpack function for each PDU type. Call the 
  appropriate pack/unpack function by means of the command_id and remove 
  pdu_type/1 function.

- Try to put the command_id back into the PDU descriptor.

- Define a couple of MACROS for every composite parameter.  One to assign
  default (record) values, and the other to hide record definition to higher
  layers.

  DEST_TELEMATICS_ID_DEFAULT_VALUE
  DEST_TELEMATICS_ID_VALUE(...)


2. Version 1.0

- Implement a gen_mc_session behavior.

- Implement a gen_mc behavior.


3. Version 2.0

- Implement a gen_re behavior.



